      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">F-305</ph> Invoice instructions.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>Contractors shall submit payment requests and receiving reports in accordance with paragraph (b) of the clause at DFARS <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="DFARS-252.232-7003" href="252.232-7003.dita#DFARS_252.232-7003">252.232-7003</xref> unless one of the exceptions in paragraph (d) of that clause applies.</p>
